uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.serial

Class FSerialiser

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.serial.FSerialiser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FSerialiserVocab
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CHierarchyParser, CHierarchyRenderer, IInstanceParser, IInstanceRenderer, IProfileSerialiser

    public class FSerialiser
extends java.lang.Object
implements FSerialiserVocab
    Provides access to the vocabulary for the standard XML serialisation of MEKON frames-model entities, via the implementation of the FSerialiserVocab interface, whilst providing a set of utility methods for performing various basic serialisation operations.
